race.description: The Bruno Suits Dress To Impress (C2) Handicap
race.comment: THROTTLE RESPONSE (3) has been knocking on the door of another victory hitting the top-four at his past five outings and strikes a very winnable contest here. Gets the services of Maloney in the irons and should be right there at the business end. SIR LAMORAK (1) placed over this distance range last time out and gets a stack of weight relief with the 3kg claim. Draws favourably and looms as the main danger. LOVEY DOVEY (4) has been thereabouts at the past couple and looks ready for the step-up in trip now. Top-three candidate. PERRI LASS (6) doesn't win out of turn but has placed at her past four starts and rarely puts in a poor one. A must for the multiples.
